1. Ona je *odbila* poziv na večeru. (She refused the invitation to dinner.)
2. *Odbila* je ponudu za posao. (She turned down the job offer.)
3. Kada sam joj predložio da idemo u kino, ona je *odbila* moj poziv. (When I suggested we go to the movies, she rejected my invitation.)
4. Prošle nedelje, automobil mi je *odbijen* na tehničkom pregledu. (Last week, my car failed the technical inspection.)
5. Njegov zahtev za povisicom plate je *odbijen*. (His request for a salary raise was rejected.)
6. Učenik je *odbio* da odgovori na pitanje nastavnika. (The student refused to answer the teacher's question.)
7. Advokat je *odbacio* optužbe protiv svog klijenta. (The lawyer dismissed the charges against his client.)
8. Ovaj lek *odbija* da deluje na mene. (This medicine is not working for me.)
9. Dama je *odbila* da sedne pored nepoznatog čoveka u autobusu. (The lady refused to sit next to a stranger on the bus.)
10. Fudbalski tim je *odbio* ponudu drugog kluba za transfer igrača. (The football team rejected another club's offer to transfer a player.)